Installation instructions for apache2 (recommended)
===================================================

* install package ($ sudo apt-get install php-saml-ds)
* install webserver with php ($ sudo apt install apache2 libapache2-mod-php)
* enable headers mod ($ sudo a2enmod headers)
* enable config ($ sudo a2enconf php-saml-ds)
* reload webserver ($ sudo service apache2 reload)
